node.text:
Presto! 🪄 Add a bit of magic to your full look transformation with #AnastasiaBeverlyHills signature staples. These base-building players upgrade any complexion routine to create a flawless, natural look. 

✨ NEW Magic Touch Concealer - With 25 shades, this buildable, medium-to-full coverage concealer gives your look the #ABHMagicTouch. This innovative formula is ultra-creamy, lightweight, and has soft-focus powders that blur imperfections. 

✨ Luminous Foundation - This water-resistant liquid foundation has a weightless wearability yet provides reliable coverage. Available in 50 shades, each leaves a radiant, natural finish. 

✨ Cream Bronzer - Adds warmth and definition with a creamy, blend-able formula that melts into the skin with ease. Sculpt and enhance your features while achieving a sun-kissed warmth.

✨ Stick Blush - Makes it easy to customize your look, whether you're going for a sheer tint or a bolder flush. This buildable formula glides on smoothly and blends seamlessly. 

✨ Stick Highlighter - This luxe, creamy formula is never gritty or flaky and can be applied almost anywhere for a megawatt shine. 

✨ Loose Setting Powder - Ready, set, BAKE! This super-fine powder caters to all your skin-setting needs. Available in 5 shades, it works to absorb oil, minimize shine, and leave your skin with a flawless matte finish.

✨ Dewy Set Setting Spray - Keeps your makeup secure with just a spritz or two, leaving skin feeling refreshed and with a fresh, dewy look all day long.
